This paper discusses the development of an Intelligent Personal Agent (IPA) that uses knowledge navigation techniques to help users gain information through reliable resources and save time. The agent is also responsible for responding to chat-based queries using Conversation Corpus. This suggests that the paper could fall under the categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Software Engineering (cs.SD).
